    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>A living blade of disaster is a @spell[blade of disaster|TCE] spell (see appendix D) with a wicked will of its own. It looks like a floating, black planar rift in the shape of a sword. Like a demon, it craves destruction.</p><p>Areas of wild magic and sites that have been ravaged by powerful eldritch forces can give rise to spell effects that become living beings. These so-called living spells haunt the places where they were created, subsisting on ambient magical energy.</p></div>",
